%% PROPOSED: Software Release Approval Sequence
sequenceDiagram
    participant SWE as SW Engineer
    participant SWL as SW Lead
    participant CI as CI
    participant PE as Project Engineer
    participant Q as Quality
    participant FO as Field Ops

    SWE->>SWL: Submit PR for release-scoped change
    SWL->>SWL: Review code and release impact
    SWL->>CI: Approve merge candidate for CI
    CI->>CI: Build and run unit or integration tests
    CI-->>SWL: Report automated test evidence
    SWL->>SWL: Approve release candidate
    SWL->>PE: Request production gate approval
    PE->>Q: Request release verification review
    Q->>Q: Check SITL, HITL, and flight evidence
    Q-->>PE: Verification complete
    PE-->>SWL: Approve production release
    SWL->>FO: Hand off released package and instructions
    FO->>FO: Deploy approved version to fleet assets

    Note over SWE,FO: Release applies across Firmware, Ignite, and Companion Computer streams
